e, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196014, "create_time": 1654698882, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 有事说事，亮明你的观点", "timestamp": 1654698882}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196019, "create_time": 1654699054, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 我的思路是：1. guan及其亲属不应该与民争利，这是guan方认可的观点；2. 现实不是这样，有部分人习以为常，还想加入，我表示不认可，不仅仅是不认可其动机，还是不认可其可能性 ，因为随着承平日久，普通人分蛋糕的可能性越来越小，这条路不是绝大多数人的出路，但是非要做于连的话也行吧；3. 我选择独善其身。", "timestamp": 1654699054}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196020, "create_time": 1654699140, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 就是纯靠垄断分流量，明明可以推动更有意义的事情", "timestamp": 1654699140}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196220, "create_time": 1654704124, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 唔，我的评价是能润尽润", "timestamp": 1654704124}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196222, "create_time": 1654704449, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 什么叫更有意义的事情，他们可不想做什么有意义的事情。维护地位，赚取利益罢了。", "timestamp": 1654704449}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196242, "create_time": 1654705706, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 润也是一个方法，像bob那样要加入，如果是小地方家族及以上还行，不然我也不建议。", "timestamp": 1654705706}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 196245, "create_time": 1654705841, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 有的还是有些进步的，至少历史上还是有进步作用的，只是做考生查成绩的生意，体验还这么差，当年的我大为震撼 。", "timestamp": 1654705841}], "create_time": 1654676526, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1654705841, "likenum": 7